WEBVTT

00:01:57.640 --> 00:02:02.920
And so I soon became familiar
with the phenomenon of the internet troll.

00:02:04.840 --> 00:02:07.376
These guys seem to live
beneath the bridges

00:02:07.400 --> 00:02:09.015
of said superhighway --

00:02:09.039 --> 00:02:12.776
(Laughter)

00:02:12.800 --> 00:02:17.000
And they also missed the memo about
the enlightenment of the internet age.

00:02:17.720 --> 00:02:20.816
I remember being called

00:02:20.840 --> 00:02:23.656
highly colorful racial slurs

00:02:23.680 --> 00:02:26.336
by those who use
the anonymity of the internet

00:02:26.360 --> 00:02:28.040
as a Klan hood.

00:02:28.560 --> 00:02:30.800
And some of them
were pretty creative, actually,